#. Tag: para
#: apps_librewriter.xml:323
#, no-c-format
msgid "&libo; comes with several predefined styles. You can use these styles as they are, modify them, or create new styles. Use the icons at the top of the panel to display formatting styles for the most common elements such as paragraphs, frames, pages or lists. To learn more about styles, continue with the instructions below."
